â
âWell, sir,â said Hilary, laughing at the terse mood of the master, âI thought you had something to say to me--a very unusual state of mind,â he was going to say, âon your part;â but stopped, with a well-bred youthâs perception of the unbecoming.
âYes, I have something to say to you.
