The lane broke out suddenly into black water; and a tall robust man stood in the twilight, with a heavy spade over his shoulder.
And Hilary Lorraine went up to him.
âNo, no, my man; not a penny to spare!
â said the Rector in anticipation; âwe have a great deal too much to do with our own poor, and with this new trouble especially.
