So you may just as well lie down--or mamma will come up with a powder for you.
â
âThe will of the Lord be done,â said Hilary; âbut, Cecil, you are getting very pretty, and you need not take away my breeches.
â
âI am sorry to do it, Cousin Hilary; but I know quite well what I am about.
And none of your military ways of going on can mislead me as to your character.
You want to be off.
We are quite aware of it.
You can scarcely put two feet to the ground.
â
âOh dear, how many ought I to be able to put?
â
âYou know best--at least four, I should hope.
